SECTION 5 ‚Äî MOBILE MONEY FRAUD (ORANGE MONEY & AFRIMONEY)
Q16: What is mobile money fraud?

A:
Mobile money fraud occurs when criminals trick Orange Money or Afrimoney users into sending money, giving out PINs, or transferring funds unknowingly.

Q17: What are common Orange Money and Afrimoney scams in Sierra Leone?

A:
Common fraud methods include:

‚ÄúYour SIM will be blocked‚Äù scam

‚ÄúYou won a promotion prize‚Äù scam

Fake agent calls asking for PIN

Fake reversal requests

Fraudsters pretending to be customer service

